headline: GTA Online
subtitle: New Hotring Circuit Races 2023
content:
Shake and bake the competition in the all new Hotring Circuit Races 2023 in GTA Online.

Buckle up and earn 3X GTA$ and RP for competing and place top 3 in any of the new Hotring Circuit 2023 tracks to receive a GTA$100,000 bonus (delivered within 72 hours of completion).
